	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">万达说“未来的影院将是娱乐综合体”，它啥意思？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-17 17:04:33 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">9</span>
